data.description: Welcome to your lakefront dream home in the heart of Cypress! This energy-efficient gem offers spacious living in a cul-de-sac. A charming brick and stone façade provides the backdrop for elegant landscaping. Step inside to a grand formal entry leading to a formal dining area and a dedicated study with french doors. A relaxing family room captivates with a stunning brick-surround fireplace and vaulted ceilings filled with abundant natural light. It joins  kitchen that has granite countertops and a seamless flow to the breakfast room. The 1st floor primary suite offers a dual sink vanity, a garden tub, and a separate shower and new flooring. Upstairs, you'll find a second primary bedroom with a huge walk-in closet, secondary bedrooms all with oversized closets, baths, and a media room. Carpet is freshly cleaned and stretched. The expansive backyard includes a covered patio, perfect for entertaining, relaxing, or gazing out to the enchanting water view. Priced below market value!
